    <subsection xml:id="Question_2_1_10">
    <title> Problem 10</title>
    <p>
        Use induction.  The key algebraic step is:

<md>
<mrow>\frac{(n-1)(3(n-1)-1)}{2}+(3n-2)\amp=\frac{(n-1)(3n-4)}{2}+(3n-2)</mrow>
<mrow>\amp=\frac{(n-1)(3n-4)+2(3n-2)}{2}</mrow>
<mrow>\amp=\frac{3n^2-n}{2}</mrow>
<mrow>\amp=\frac{n(3n-1)}{2}</mrow>
</md>
    </p>
</subsection>

 <subsection xml:id="Question_2_1_11">
    <title> Problem 11</title>
    <ol marker="(a)">
        <li>
